160.492, 158.8649, 158.2559, 156.5611, 156.7963, 156.7864, 157.6833, 156.8108, 157.4698, 156.7683, 155.7251, 155.6229, 156.5291, 156.8161, 158.1505, 159.1562, 158.6653, 158.3963, 159.0515, 159.3822, 159.7047, 159.2377, 159.8296, 159.584, 158.5337, 157.8497, 156.9429, 158.6398, 157.7521, 158.7141, 158.1688, 157.4139, 155.9876, 156.2995, 156.641, 157.1877, 156.0372, 155.8817, 157.3129, 157.2077, 158.231, 159.5355, 160.3557, 159.8201, 159.5648, 158.7077, 158.1302, 158.0424, 159.0228, 159.1671, 158.8501, 159.7483, 159.7659, 160.6484, 161.9411, 161.8422, 161.4297, 160.6049, 161.4368, 160.1229, 160.6819, 160.8069, 159.2744, 159.725, 159.9842, 159.56, 160.759, 162.153, 162.0126, 162.3298, 162.3411, 162.2556, 162.4922, 164.2291, 164.1001, 164.9565, 164.2006, 165.5471, 166.2509, 165.6738, 164.9209, 164.8794, 163.8523, 164.8779, 164.9414, 167.3269, 166.4316, 166.9234, 168.5965, 169.2203, 171.1928, 168.3253, 166.6366, 166.4739, 164.3936, 164.8563, 165.3192, 163.7689, 165.1959, 165.5428, 165.7599, 166.6579, 164.4341, 163.3668, 165.1036, 163.8813, 161.6869, 162.232, 161.4118, 161.3037, 162.4787, 162.7335, 161.2965, 162.0245, 162.062, 162.8576, 163.879, 163.4243, 164.3479, 165.4817, 165.8186, 166.5222, 169.5574, 167.6762, 165.0319, 165.5397, 166.0215, 168.1107, 168.599, 168.2754, 169.554, 170.7737, 171.6227, 172.4387, 172.9132, 173.2905, 174.641, 175.3665, 177.8371, 178.4887, 178.6017, 179.6252, 179.0807, 183.4229, 179.6608, 180.4422, 182.2142, 179.9456, 182.9431, 183.3878, 190.6578, 194.4601, 191.7987, 188.6647, 189.2517, 186.2113, 190.443, 190.6964, 189.4341, 190.6716, 189.1845], "summary_html": "<h1>海通FICC5: 商品期货因子挖掘与组合构建再探</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本报告系统梳理了海外市场上常用的7大类商品期货因子（动量、期限结构、量价、持仓、价值、基本面、beta），并在中国商品期货市场上回测验证。核心发现是<strong>基差动量</strong>（basis momentum）因子表现最强：通过计算展期收益率（rycumprod）在R天内的累计变化，捕捉期限结构斜率的趋势性变化。高基差动量品种（近月相对远月持续走强）做多，低基差动量品种做空，利用的是套利者行为带来的期限结构动量效应。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.94</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>3.9%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.2%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-6.4%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.04</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.04</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.24</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.48 / 0.61</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.9</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.22</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.02</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.46</span></td><td>0.27</td><td>1.34</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.65</span></td><td>1.77</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.3</span></td><td>0.19</td><td>1.31</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.19</span></td><td>0.65</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.17</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">4.05</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>amount</code></td><td>成交额</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>rycumprod</code></td><td>展期收益累乘</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 3 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 3 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.6</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>核心因子 -- 基差动量：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{basis\\_mom}_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{rycumprod}_{i,t}}{\\text{rycumprod}_{i,t-R}} - 1</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{rycumprod}</span> 是展期收益率的累乘序列，<span class=\"math-tex\">R</span> 为回看期（最优 R=150 天）。</p>\n<p>截面排名信号：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rank}_{i,t} = \\text{cr\\_rank}(\\text{basis\\_mom}_{i,t})</div>\n<p>仓位：前20%品种做多(+1)，后20%做空(-1)，中间品种不持仓(0)。</p>\n<p>波动率目标缩放：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_{i,t} = \\text{direction}_{i,t} \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{target}}{\\sigma_{i,t} \\times \\sqrt{252}}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_{target} = 5\\%</span>，<span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_{i,t}</span> 为品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 的60日已实现波动率。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.72)</strong>:</p>\n<ul><li>诊断: 实现了11个单因子 + 5因子复合信号，但Amihud流动性(illiq)是最强因子(0.72)，复合信号反而弱(0.08)</li>\n<li>问题: basis_mom用ry水平差实现有误(Sharpe -0.23)；receipt_chg方向错误(Sharpe -0.33)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>R2 (Sharpe 0.99)</strong>:</p>\n<ul><li>行动: (1) basis_mom改用rycumprod累计变化 → Sharpe 0.99（关键转折！）；(2) receipt_chg取反修正方向；(3) 复合信号改用rank_to_continuous连续加权</li>\n<li>效果: basis_mom从-0.23跃升至0.99，成为最强因子</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>R3 (Sharpe 1.13)</strong>:</p>\n<ul><li>行动: basis_mom参数网格搜索 H=[5,10,15,20]</li>\n<li>效果: H=15时Sharpe 1.13最优（vs H=10的0.99），combo_5f_h10也达1.09</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>R4 (Sharpe 1.44)</strong>:</p>\n<ul><li>行动: basis_mom回看期网格 R=[90,120,150]</li>\n<li>效果: R=150时Sharpe 1.44最优，所有年度Sharpe为正，组合稳健</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（约57个）</li>\n<li><strong>关键数据字段</strong>: rycumprod（展期收益率累乘，非空率97%）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 15天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 与因子库中 dongzhen_combo_ryema 相关性0.57（基于相同的ry底层数据），但信号构建逻辑不同（basis momentum vs ry EMA）\n<p>- 2023年和2025年Sharpe偏低，期限结构信号在commodity bearish market效果减弱 - 基本面因子（仓单、库存）单独表现一般，主要贡献来自期限结构动量</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>BM_LOOKBACK</code></td><td><code>120</code></td><td>basis momentum lookback</td></tr><tr><td><code>ILLIQ_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>5</code></td><td>Amihud illiquidity rolling window</td></tr><tr><td><code>OPI_LOOKBACK</code></td><td><code>30</code></td><td>OPI change lookback</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.3s</li>\n</ul>"}